keshi.list <- str_extract_all(a$detail, "[0-9]+")
get.keshi <- function(keshi.words) {
  if (length(keshi.words) > 0){
    str_extract(keshi.words, "[0-9]+") %>% as.integer() %>% max()
  } else {
    # ,  NA
    NA
  }
}

  sqrt(mean((pred-gt)^2, na.rm=T))
}
